Description: Simulation and analysis of quantitative traits within breeding populations.
    ViSAGE provides an interactive interface for users to
    1. Simulate quantitative traits with additive, dominance, and epistasis architectures.
    2. Conduct multi-generation selection using either a directional, stabilizing or diruptive selection type.
    3. Conduct genome-wide association studies (GWAS) and genome-wide prediction analyses.
